            "body": "I download and build the version 0.12 with the commit above and I am still having the same error:\n```\nvim.schedule callback: /usr/local/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/lsp/util.lua:1977: attempt to concatenate field 'containerName' (a userdata value)\nstack traceback:\n\t/usr/local/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/lsp/util.lua:1977: in function 'symbols_to_items'\n\t...nvim/lazy/telescope.nvim/lua/telescope/builtin/__lsp.lua:338: in function 'handler'\n\t/usr/local/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/lsp/client.lua:742: in function 'fn'\n\t[string \"vim/_core/editor\"]:273: in function <[string \"vim/_core/editor\"]:272>\n```\n\n```\nnvim -v                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         6m 51.254s\nNVIM v0.12.3-dev-34+g378f5f49b3\nBuild type: RelWithDebInfo\nLuaJIT 2.1.1774638290\nRun \"nvim -V1 -v\" for more info\n```\n\nAnything that I can do to prevent it?",
